The goal is to improve the performance of `ByteUtils.sizeOfUnsignedVarint` and `ByteUtils.sizeOfVarlong` by replacing loop-based bit shifting with branchless computations using `Integer.numberOfLeadingZeros` and `Long.numberOfLeadingZeros`. These are intrinsic methods that compile to fast CPU instructions, eliminating loop overhead and branching.

